
# 🛍️ Myntra Clone

This is a fully responsive **Myntra Clone** created using **HTML**, **CSS**, and **JavaScript**. It replicates the core features and user interface of the popular Indian fashion e-commerce platform, **Myntra**, for learning and demonstration purposes.

## 🔥 Features

- ✅ Responsive Home Page with Banners
- ✅ Product Listing Page (PLP)
- ✅ Product Detail Page (PDP)
- ✅ Add to Cart Functionality
- ✅ Local Storage-based Cart Management


## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- **HTML5** – For page structure  
- **CSS3** – For styling and responsive layout  
- **JavaScript (ES6)** – For interactivity and dynamic cart functionality  

