## 🚀 Getting Started

1. Clone the repo:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/yourusername/myntra-clone.git
   ```
2. Navigate into the project folder:
   ```bash
   cd myntra-clone
   ```
3. Open `index.html` in your browser.

## 📁 Folder Structure

```
myntra-clone/
├── index.html
├── product.html
├── cart.html
├── css/
│   └── styles.css
├── js/
│   └── script.js
├── assets/
│   └── images/
```

